title: [Admission] Guys any idea on how many seats are surrenderd under jee and around how many will be called for kcet ?

comments.body: Very few seats have been surrendered. Hence jee round 2 counselling has been cancelled. This was the update given by admissions dept when went to college yesterday
Are u sure bcz I heard lot of seats are surrenderd
All the surrendered seats will be used for the pes kcet counselling scheduled on 20th
